<plot>This Flemish sitcom is the n-th version (originally a single theatre play, later screen adaptations) of a classical Flemish story, rather like Laurel and Hardy, about two inseparable friends. Slisse is fat, wealthy, educated, his mate Cesar measly, poor and ignorant; anything they touch goes sour, so they frequently bicker, not in the least because Slisse must explain everything painstakingly to Cesar, who always gets the wrong end of the stick, but still they just can't do without each-other.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?501756</url></doc>
